copyright: ICU is released under a nonrestrictive open source license that is suitable for use with both commercial software and with other open source or free software.
description: ICU is a mature, widely used set of C/C++ and Java libraries providing Unicode and Globalization support for software applications. ICU is widely portable and gives applications the same results on all platforms and between C/C++ and Java software. This is a NuGet package of ICU built with/for Visual Studio 2015.
releaseNotes: CLDR 31, Emoji 5.0 draft data, C++11 support, Java number formatting code rewrite.
